Package: mikrom-router-caddy
Version: 0.1.0
Section: httpd
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Mikrom Team <team@mikrom.local>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), libssl3
Conflicts: caddy
Provides: caddy, httpd
Description: Custom Caddy build with Mikrom dynamic routing plugin.
 This package provides a Caddy binary pre-compiled with the mikrom-router-caddy
 plugin for dynamic NATS-based routing and ACME challenge handling.
